"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-21-keeping-cool-managing-emotions-cheering-olympic-heroes\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"AS Jamaica tunes in to the Olympic Games, excitement will fill the air.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 71, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999986415805456, \"rank\": 1.2490261024487676e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 40}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 52}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 70}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans will eagerly watch their favourite athletes compete on the grandest stage, but with high stakes come intense emotions.\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"their favourite athletes\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"the grandest stage\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"high stakes\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 172}, {\"ngram\": \"intense emotions\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From joy to anxiety, cheering for our sports heroes can lead to an emotional roller coaster.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"our sports heroes\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional roller coaster\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's how to manage those feelings and make the most of this thrilling experience, Jamaican style!\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.7084983575203305, \"rank\": 0.4114241640929433, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those feelings\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 324}, {\"ngram\": \"this thrilling experience\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1) EMBRACE THE EMOTION First and foremost, it's essential to accept that strong emotions are part of being a fan.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"THE EMOTION\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"strong emotions\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it's elation after a gold medal win or heartbreak from a narrow defeat, allow yourself to feel.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elation\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal win\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"a narrow defeat\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Acknowledging these emotions can enhance your viewing experience, making it more memorable and authentic.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these emotions\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"your viewing experience\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2) CELEBRATE WITH SOUND In Jamaica, the energy of watching sports often involves lively celebrations.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999986415805456, \"rank\": 1.2490261024487676e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SOUND\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"lively celebrations\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From blowing vuvuzelas to clanging pot covers, fans express their excitement with enthusiasm.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"vuvuzelas\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"clanging\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"pot covers\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"their excitement\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiasm\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These sounds not only amplify the atmosphere but also serve as a great way to channel those emotions.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"a great way\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"those emotions\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So grab your instruments and make some noise!\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your instruments\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"some noise\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3) PRACTISE MINDFULNESS When the pressure mounts, mindfulness can help ground you.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"MINDFULNESS\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"mindfulness\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a few deep breaths before the event begins, focusing on the rhythm of your breath.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few deep breaths\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"the rhythm\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"your breath\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you start feeling overwhelmed during a competition, pause for a moment to refocus.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simple techniques, like counting to 10 or visualising a calm place, can reduce anxiety and keep you centred.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simple techniques\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"a calm place\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"4) SHARE THE EXPERIENCE Watching the Olympics with friends or family can amplify the joy and lessen the stress.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"THE EXPERIENCE\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the stress\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share your excitement, discuss performances, and celebrate wins together.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your excitement\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"discuss\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"performances\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"wins\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The camaraderie of being with fellow fans provides support and makes the emotional journey more enjoyable.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The camaraderie\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow fans\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional journey\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And do not forget to bring out the drum or any musical instrument for that extra flair!\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the drum\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"any musical instrument\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"that extra flair\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"5) BALANCE YOUR VIEWING HABITS While it's tempting to immerse yourself completely in Olympic coverage, consider balancing your viewing habits.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"YOUR VIEWING HABITS\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic coverage\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"your viewing habits\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Set limits on how much time you spend glued to the screen.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Set limits\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"how much time\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the screen\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Engaging in other activities, such as going for a walk or reading, can provide much-needed breaks and help manage heightened emotions.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other activities\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"a walk\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"reading\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"much-needed breaks\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"heightened emotions\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"6) KEEP PERSPECTIVE While it's easy to get caught up in the moment, remember that sports are unpredictable.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PERSPECTIVE\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes train tirelessly, but outcomes are never guaranteed.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"outcomes\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Keeping a healthy perspective allows you to appreciate the thrill of competition without becoming too emotionally invested in the results.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a healthy perspective\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the thrill\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"7) REFLECT AND RELEASE After an event, take a moment to reflect on your emotions.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"7) REFLECT\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"RELEASE\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"your emotions\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What made you feel joyful or anxious?\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Writing down your thoughts or discussing them with others can be therapeutic.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your thoughts\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Acknowledging and releasing these feelings can enhance your overall experience and prepare you for the next event.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these feelings\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"your overall experience\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"the next event\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympic Games unfold, remember that while the competition brings highs and lows, managing your emotions can help you savour every moment.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"highs\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"lows\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"your emotions\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So cheer loudly, clang those pot covers, blow your vuvuzelas, and enjoy the extraordinary journey of the Olympic spirit!\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your vuvuzelas\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"the extraordinary journey\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Robiann Broomfield recently completed her PhD and has finished her clinical internship at Baylor College of Medicine/TIRR Memorial Hermann Hospital, where she focused on rehabilitation psychology and neuropsychology.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3072, \"end\": 3082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999940082489, \"rank\": 5.863821481260605e-09, \"text\": \"Broomfield\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her PhD\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"her clinical internship\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"Baylor College\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"Medicine/TIRR Memorial Hermann Hospital\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"rehabilitation psychology\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"neuropsychology\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In September, she will further her expertise with a fellowship in neuropsychology at Harvard Medical School.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3366, \"end\": 3388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_Medical_School\", \"score\": 0.9999996995484705, \"rank\": 3.0045179496379354e-07, \"text\": \"Harvard Medical School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_Medical_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_Medical_School\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"her expertise\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"a fellowship\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3343}, {\"ngram\": \"neuropsychology\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Broomfield is passionate about advancing mental health care and contributing to the understanding of cognitive processes in rehabilitation settings.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999940082489, \"rank\": 5.863821481260605e-09, \"text\": \"Broomfield\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broomfield_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mental health care\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3452}, {\"ngram\": \"the understanding\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3490}, {\"ngram\": \"cognitive processes\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"rehabilitation settings\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3554}]}]}"